{"tid":19114,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"強姦逾10未成年少女 淫官被處死","createTime":"2016-12-02T15:40:27.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-03T01:58:25.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0914dc9296dc713eb955a08a21b969e0ad82981e","tid":19114,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T15:40:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20130619/large/1371613322_5a1a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20130619%2Flarge%2F1371613322_5a1a.jpg&h=dcaac12c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n河南省永城市委辦公室原副主任李新功，涉嫌姦淫10多名未成年少女，早前被裁定強姦及猥褻兒童罪名成立，昨日被執行死刑。<br />\n<br />\n去年5月，有網友發帖爆料稱，河南永城市官員李新功姦淫未成年少女被捕，並指「李新功姦淫未成年少女數十名，罪行極大，手段惡劣」。多日後，當地官方證實李新功因涉嫌強姦未成年女性10多名，已被公安機關刑事拘留。<br />\n<br />\n李新功被逮捕後，交由河南省商丘市中級人民法院進行一審，並被裁定干犯強姦罪及猥褻兒童罪，兩罪合併決定執行死刑，剝奪政治權利終身。李新功曾提出上訴，但被河南省高級人民法院駁回。最高人民法院經複核，核准對李新功執行死刑。"},{"pid":"66b92b1b952471fab9d6303293df91ac54313ebd","tid":19114,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T15:44:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"14b56cd8c5429f7931c5bd75a74842d7bf6daac0","tid":19114,"uid":14744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T15:54:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食10幾個處，<span style=\"color: red;\">死而無憾</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同埋應該係死不足惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ae5967b39c682a88806f5e47e7ddf82636a1396","tid":19114,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T16:29:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42cab48b29df2ab113b68edfc739fa659be42f80","tid":19114,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T01:56:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b570587d53ca5bc712aee942283dd0c762198fe","tid":19114,"uid":41509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T01:58:25.000Z","msg":"係咪<br />\n掩口費俾唔夠？呢d 野無鬼邊死得人"}]}